te autumn bats continued to roost in the shed with day temperatures rising above 30\u00b0C, compared with unoccupied caves, which were considerably cooler at this time (~20\u00b0C). Clarification of the estimated energy savings and the possible costs in terms of milk production requires further research to measure concurrently body temperatures, roost temperature and energy expenditure, together with juvenile growth in different types of roosts.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Law, B. S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chidel, M.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/628d094eaa2d14b20879be5edf603ec9", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/3ec614f15754ac052bbc6891a97f5e43f9625951e3caa7ba4fce9df2f850130c", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/YZTLWVZP", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/YZTLWVZP", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/57bce583d79caf6a14fe8414bb62c288!/b22269-24826", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "49", "title": "Australian Journal of Zoology", "volume": "55"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/628d094eaa2d14b20879be5edf603ec9"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545